        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Introduction</h2><p>Few diamonds capture light and legacy quite like the Portuguese Cut Diamond. Known for its deep brilliance and intricate faceting, this vintage cut combines history, artistry, and technical mastery in one exceptional gemstone. Its captivating symmetry and unparalleled sparkle make it a favorite among collectors and modern jewelry enthusiasts alike.</p><p>At Lucira Jewelry, we believe true luxury lies in the union of brilliance and responsibility. The Portuguese Cut Diamond embodies this balance perfectly — a radiant blend of timeless beauty and contemporary ethics through our innovative<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-jewellery\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond jewellery</span></a> craftsmanship.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Is the Portuguese Cut Diamond?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What Is the Portuguese Cut Diamond?</h2>",
            "custom_id": "22carat"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JmwFBb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Portuguese D",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The Portuguese Diamond Cut is distinguished by its exceptional faceting — typically 161 to 200 facets compared to the 57 or 58 facets of most modern cuts. This intricate design maximizes light reflection, resulting in extraordinary fire and depth.</p><p>Unlike conventional diamond cuts that prioritize simplicity and uniformity, the Portuguese Cut celebrates complexity. Its high crown, small table, and deep pavilion create layers of light play, giving the diamond an almost three-dimensional glow. This cut is a testament to the artistry of traditional gem cutting — where every facet is placed with intention to amplify the stone’s natural radiance.</p><h2>The History Behind the Portuguese Diamond Cut</h2><p>The origins of the Portuguese Diamond Cut trace back to 18th-century Europe, where royal families and noble collectors sought the most brilliant diamonds available. Believed to have first emerged in Portugal’s historic gem-cutting houses, the cut soon became a symbol of prestige and sophistication.</p><p>As diamond design evolved, the Portuguese Cut became rarer, reserved for select stones that showcased perfect clarity and symmetry. Today, Lucira Jewelry reimagines this heritage through<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond rings</span></a>, preserving the legacy of craftsmanship while embracing sustainability and ethical sourcing.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jc4E4r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Anatomy of Brilliance: What Makes It So Special",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Anatomy of Brilliance: What Makes It So Special</h2><h3>Exceptional Faceting</h3><p>The Portuguese Cut features a unique concentric arrangement of facets that enhance its internal fire. With nearly three times the number of facets found in a standard cut, it produces a mesmerizing light performance.</p><h3>Depth and Dimension</h3><p>The deep pavilion and elevated crown allow light to travel through multiple planes, resulting in an unparalleled depth of sparkle.</p><h3>Elevated Crown and Smaller Table</h3><p>The smaller table emphasizes the diamond’s brilliance, while the raised crown provides a regal, domed effect — ideal for statement jewelry and heirloom pieces.</p><p>Each Portuguese Cut Diamond<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-for-women\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> engagement ring for women</span></a> from Lucira is precisely crafted to highlight these defining characteristics, ensuring a rare balance of brilliance and elegance.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": "importance"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6WCWXy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Portuguese Cut Diamond vs Round Brilliant",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Portuguese Cut Diamond vs Round Brilliant</h2><p>The Portuguese Cut Diamond vs Round Brilliant comparison reveals a clear distinction: while the Round Brilliant prioritizes balance and uniformity, the Portuguese Cut celebrates depth and individuality. For those who appreciate rare craftsmanship and vintage allure, the Portuguese Cut offers a touch of exclusivity unmatched by mass-market designs.</p><p>Explore this brilliance redefined — discover Lucira’s handcrafted<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond</span></a> cuts that reflect both tradition and innovation.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": "components"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_AWtNat": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Why Lab Grown Diamonds Are the Future of Fine Jewelry",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>Lab-Grown Portuguese Cut Diamonds: The Perfect Blend of Ethics and Excellence</h2><p>Lucira Jewelry’s Lab Grown Portuguese Cut Diamonds represent the future of fine jewelry — combining advanced technology with artistic heritage. By cultivating diamonds in controlled laboratory environments, we recreate the same physical, chemical, and optical properties of natural diamonds without the environmental cost of mining.</p><h3>Benefits of Lab Grown Portuguese Cut Diamonds</h3><ul><li>Zero mining impact: Each diamond is grown ethically, without disturbing ecosystems.<br/><br/></li><li>Certified quality: Every Lucira diamond is IGI-certified, ensuring authenticity and transparency.<br/><br/></li><li>Accessible luxury: Lab grown diamonds provide exceptional brilliance at a fraction of the traditional price.<br/><br/></li></ul><p>This evolution allows you to own a piece of timeless beauty — responsibly created and ethically sourced.</p><h2>The Portuguese Cut Diamond Ring: Vintage Charm With Modern Design</h2><p>A Portuguese Cut Diamond Ring is more than jewelry; it is a statement of sophistication. Lucira Jewelry combines the vintage artistry of the Portuguese Cut with contemporary design sensibilities.</p><p>Whether it’s a classic solitaire, a delicate halo, or an elegant side-stone setting, the Portuguese Cut’s deep brilliance enhances every design. Each ring, including<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/couple-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> couple rings</span></a>, is handcrafted to reflect individuality — perfect for engagements, anniversaries, or meaningful milestones.</p><p>At Lucira, our rings are not just worn; they’re experienced — created with precision, passion, and purpose.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Choose Your Portuguese Diamond Cut",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Choose Your Portuguese Diamond Cut</h2><h3>Cut Precision</h3><p>Choose a diamond with precise symmetry and proportion. The intricate faceting demands expert craftsmanship for maximum light performance.</p><h3>Carat and Proportion</h3><p>The depth of the Portuguese Cut may slightly reduce surface area, so balance carat weight with proportion for optimal brilliance.</p><h3>Metal Setting</h3><p>Platinum and white gold settings complement the diamond’s reflective geometry, while yellow gold offers a warm, vintage contrast.</p><h3>Certification & Trust</h3><p>Every Lucira diamond comes with an IGI Certification, ensuring quality and traceability. To explore your perfect stone, book a virtual consultation with our jewelry specialists.</p><h2>Caring for Your Portuguese Cut Diamond</h2><p>To maintain the brilliance of your Portuguese Cut Diamond, regular care is essential:</p><ul><li>Clean gently using mild soap and warm water.<br/><br/></li><li>Avoid harsh chemicals that may dull the facets.<br/><br/></li><li>Schedule professional cleaning through Lucira’s Lifetime Exchange and Care Program.<br/><br/></li></ul><p>With thoughtful care, your diamond will remain as radiant as the day it was created.</p><h2>The Future of the Portuguese Cut</h2><p>The global jewelry landscape is undergoing a remarkable transformation. Today’s conscious consumers seek more than just beauty — they desire pieces that embody their values as well as their style. The lab-grown Portuguese Cut Diamond perfectly captures this shift, blending sustainability with timeless sophistication.</p><p>At Lucira Jewelry, we are redefining what luxury means. Each piece we create carries a story of purpose, progress, and purity. The Portuguese Cut is not just a nod to the past; it is a vision for the future — where every facet shines with integrity.</p><h2>Conclusion: A Legacy of Light</h2><p>The Portuguese Cut Diamond stands as a symbol of brilliance, artistry, and ethics — a perfect harmony of history and innovation. For those who seek a diamond as rare as their love, Lucira Jewelry offers creations that embody both conscience and craftsmanship.</p><p>Design your own<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond rings</span></a> today. Book a free virtual consultation or visit our Experience Store to bring your dream ring to life — where brilliance meets responsibility.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": "check"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ADDTPa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How Lab-Grown ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How Lab-Grown Diamonds Are Made — Everything You Need to Know</h2><p>If you’ve ever wanted to see how lab grown diamonds are made, Lucira offers you the opportunity to learn through our educational guides and virtual consultations. Our experts walk you through the entire process — from diamond growth to crafting the perfect piece.</p><p>Each Lucira creation reflects innovation, integrity, and artistry. Visit our experience store or schedule a video consultation to witness the brilliance of<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/1-carat-lab-grown-diamond-price-in-india\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> 1 carat lab grown diamond price in India</span></a> firsthand.</p><ul><li><h3>Lab Grown Diamonds vs. Simulants: Clearing the Confusion</h3></li></ul><p>It’s important to understand that lab grown diamonds are not the same as diamond simulants like cubic zirconia or moissanite. Simulants only resemble diamonds in appearance but differ in composition and properties.</p><p>Lab grown diamonds, on the other hand, are made of pure carbon, just like natural diamonds. They score a perfect 10 on the Mohs scale of hardness and possess the same sparkle and fire that make diamonds so desirable.</p><p>When you choose Lucira, you’re choosing real diamonds — just made responsibly.</p><ul><li><h3>Lab Grown Diamonds: How They Are Made to Last a Lifetime</h3></li></ul><p>Each Lucira diamond is crafted to last a lifetime. The advanced processes of HPHT and CVD ensure structural integrity and unmatched brilliance. Our designs, made with precious metals and expert craftsmanship, transform these diamonds into heirlooms meant to be cherished forever.</p><p>At Lucira Jewelry, every creation embodies our promise: crafted to last, designed to shine. Explore our curated<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/earrings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> earrings</span></a> and<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/earrings-for-men\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> earrings for men</span></a> for timeless pieces.</p><h3>Conclusion</h3><p>Understanding how lab grown diamonds are made reveals more than just a scientific marvel; it reflects a conscious choice for a better future. These diamonds represent love, innovation, and responsibility — values that define modern luxury.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry</span></a> continues to lead India’s ethical jewelry movement, combining precision technology with timeless craftsmanship. Because true beauty should never come at the planet’s expense.</p><p>Now that you understand lab-grown diamond creation, explore Lucira’s exclusive collection of certified, ethical, and handcrafted<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond jewellery</span></a> — from engagement rings to elegant necklaces, each piece tells a story of brilliance and responsibility.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_id": "buying"
          }
        }
